{
  "stem": "22856.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second interest was I organized a school shop with stationary on a cheaper way to save some money for my friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The third idea was, because I liked to fly, but only in my dreams.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a club in our school, and we collected money for gliders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were only two schools who were interested in gliders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One of them was our school, and because we collected a lot of money for the first glider, we received a free flight from Cracow to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was the happy one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was in the year 1935, shortly before my matriculation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In some cases.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one or two cases that professors sometimes gave us idea that he's not our friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But generally speaking, that wasn't allowed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Officially, there was no antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we came to the university, it was a much stronger problem, because there were days without Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once I came to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] university, I took part in the lecture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Suddenly a bell stopped a professor of-- of his lecture and, from the back, came one student and told me, friend, today is a day without Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to leave it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I knew that there were excesses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some violence in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a Nazi-- one Nazi type of party in Poland, the Nationals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had the chance sometimes, unofficially, to make some perturbance-- turbulence I would say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, we were too young, and univer-- these colleges did not allow us to take part or belong to any political clubs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had our Jewish connections, especially with a type of early Zionist.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
